# GatewayTransferNative.sol 状态转换漏洞审计报告

## 概述

本文档详细分析了 GatewayTransferNative.sol 合约中的状态转换漏洞。这些漏洞可能导致合约状态不一致、资金损失或其他安全问题。

## 1. externalId 生成逻辑漏洞

### 问题描述

在 `_calcExternalId` 函数中，`externalId` 的计算使用了 `block.timestamp` 作为其中一个参数：

```solidity
function _calcExternalId(address sender) internal view returns (bytes32 externalId) {
    externalId = keccak256(abi.encodePacked(address(this), sender, globalNonce, block.timestamp));
}
```

### 漏洞分析

codex
I’ve got a concrete non-duplicate high now: both ZEVM gateways let anyone steal any pending non-EVM refund because `claimRefund()` defaults the payout target to the caller. I’m verifying one last gateway-compatibility issue in `GatewaySend.onCall()` against the imported Zeta interface so I can keep the final set tight and defensible.
